reviewText: The title says it all....... AMAZING! Beautiful to watch & perfect music paired with it!

What a collection! A cd of truly beautiful music, AND a breathtaking dvd/blu-ray of magnificent Hubble images... These are not static pictures of space, or even  camera panning shots - SOMEHOW the  filmaker zooms into the skyfield itself, and wraps the image around you! It's not IMAX 3-d, but sure bears any other Hubble videos I've ever seen. This is a true basket of goodies, that should not be passed by...
